    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes some of the procedures, scoring and tests used in the TCP and IP bake offs held in the early development of these protocols.  These procedures and tests may still be of use in testing newly implemented TCP and IP modules.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
